#

Crispy Fish Burger

25 min
$12.99
650 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

FishEggWheat

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carbohydrate

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

EasyQuickComfort Food

Description

A delicious fish burger with a crispy coating, served with fresh toppings for a satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • white fish fillet (like cod or haddock): 2 pieces
  • burger buns: 2
  • shredded lettuce: 1 cup
  • tomato slices: 4 slices
  • mayonnaise: 2 tablespoons
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
  • flour: 1/2 cup
  • egg: 1, beaten
  • breadcrumbs: 1 cup
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • paprika: 1 teaspoon
